        <%= image_tag "mcone.png", :class => "journey img-fluid justify-content-center" %>
        <h5  style="margin-bottom: 60px">First main change - when user creates profile, on the screen will get personalized welcome greeting. Based on their orders, and wishlish will see the “just for you” recomendation. Also categories are displayed in a way that user on mobile phone can see clearly category options. I added new feature by clicking on a heart add favorite products to a wishlist with sharing option</h5>
        <%= image_tag "mctwo.png", :class => "journey img-fluid justify-content-center" %>
        <h5 style="margin-bottom: 60px">In the category section I created microinteraction - horizontal scrollbar, to keep the website more engaging, which positively contributing to the look-and-feel of a product</h5>
         <%= image_tag "mcthree.png", :class => "journey img-fluid justify-content-center" %>
        <h5 style="margin-bottom: 60px">Stars on the original website could be confusing, because it is not possible to rating the product. Instead I added reviews. In case user don’t find suitable product, can look into a similar products which is placed on the bottom of the page</h5>
